    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or reliable transportation for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the roof and trunk. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak shape. It\u2019s a dependable car that has been used regularly, offered at a price that reflects its current state.",
