      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely stunning, showroom-quality vehicle! This car is in truly mint condition, meticulously maintained and looking as pristine as the day it first rolled off the lot. From the flawless exterior finish to the spotless interior, every detail has been cared for with the utmost pride. If you're looking for a top-tier driving experience in a vehicle that looks and feels brand new, this is the perfect gem for you!",
