      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project or a source of parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy oxidation on the paint, several deep scratches, and noticeable rust bubbling along the wheel arches and door sills. Inside, the upholstery has multiple tears and deep staining, and some of the dashboard electronics are non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention due to a persistent oil leak and a rough idle, while the suspension feels quite loose. Please expect to invest time and resources into repairs to make this car roadworthy and reliable again.",
